nhwIssue 24  nhk(Feb 1989)
nc  The E911 issue. "Control Office Administration of Enhanced 911 Service"
nc  by The Eavesdropper -- the document that triggered Operation Sundevil
nc  and led directly to the founding of the Electronic Frontier Foundation.
nw  13 philes including both E911 articles.

nhwIssue 72  nhk(Aug 2025)
nc  40 years of Phrack. 19 philes: PHP exploitation, macOS IOKit,
nc  WebAssembly sandboxing, Rsync RCE, quantum ROP, CPU backdoors,
nc  a Prophile on Gera, and The Hacker's Renaissance: A Manifesto Reborn.

